#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Philip's Approach**:\n"
"- Uses Claude Desktop exclusively\n"
"- Views code through Dev UI's workspace browser\n"
"- Treats the agent as a soundboard for design discussions\n"
"- Runs multiple Claude instances for different tasks\n"
"- Rarely opens a traditional IDE"
msgstr "*Philip 的方法* ： - 完全使用 Claude Desktop - 通过 Dev UI 的工作区浏览器查看代码 - 将代理视为设计讨论的声板 - 为不同任务运行多个 Claude 实例 - 很少打开传统的集成开发环境"

