#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Max's Approach**:\n"
"- Prefers https://github.com/Pythagora-io/gpt-pilot[GPT Pilot]\n"
"- Focuses on incremental development\n"
"- Uses plan mode but avoids over-planning\n"
"- Emphasizes iterative refinement"
msgstr "*马克斯的方法* ： - 更倾向于 link:https://github.com/Pythagora-io/gpt-pilot[GPT 试点] - 侧重于渐进式开发 - 使用计划模式，但避免过度计划 - 强调迭代改进"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Eric's Approach**:\n"
"- Uses IntelliJ with Claude integration\n"
"- Leverages IDE context sensitivity\n"
"- Benefits from IDE's diff viewer\n"
"- Combines IDE refactoring with AI generation"
msgstr "*Eric 的方法* ： - 使用与 Claude 集成的 IntelliJ - 利用集成开发环境的上下文敏感性 - 受益于集成开发环境的差异查看器 - 将集成开发环境重构与人工智能生成相结合"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Holly's Approach**:\n"
"- Swaps between Claude Code and Bob\n"
"- Uses Test-Driven Development (TDD) with agents\n"
"- Writes tests first, then has agent implement\n"
"- Finds TDD particularly effective for reproducers"
msgstr "*霍利的方法* ： - 在克劳德代码和鲍勃之间交换 - 与代理一起使用测试驱动开发（TDD） - 先编写测试，然后让代理执行 - 发现 TDD 对再现器特别有效"

